# Green Haven Plant Shop - React Redux E-commerce Project

This is a frontend e-commerce application for a plant shop built with React and Redux. It demonstrates modern web development practices including state management with Redux Toolkit, routing with React Router, and responsive design.

## Features

### Landing Page
- Attractive background image
- Company name and description
- Get Started button linking to product listing

### Header
- Displayed on both product and cart pages
- Navigation links
- Shopping cart icon with dynamic count

### Product Listing Page
- Six unique houseplants displayed with images, names, and prices
- Plants grouped into three categories
- Add to Cart button that:
  - Increments the cart count when clicked
  - Gets disabled after being clicked
  - Adds the plant to the shopping cart

### Shopping Cart Page
- Displays total number of plants in cart
- Calculates and shows total cost
- Each plant shows thumbnail, name, and unit price
- Increase/decrease buttons for each plant
- Delete button to remove plants
- Checkout button (displays "Coming Soon" message)
- Continue Shopping button to return to products

## Technologies Used

- React 18
- Redux Toolkit for state management
- React Router for navigation
- CSS for styling

